item.title: HTB - Ready
item.description: Ready Contents Write Up Recon Credentials Notes Write Up Two open ports, 22 and a web server on 5080. The web server is hosting an instance of GitLab. Signing up works without verification and lets me onto the GitLab dashboard. There’s one public project called ready-channel, created by user “dude”. The project repo houses a drupal install and we pick up some mysql credentials(drupaluser : %%cHzhNC=k9yYN!T) from the settings.
